Function for Minutes Played¶

In [29]:
def Minutesplot(playerlist=Players):
    Col = {"CJMcCollum":"Black","DevinBooker":"Red","DonovanMitchell":"Green","JimmyButler":"Blue","LouWilliams":"Magenta","BradleyBeal":"Black","DeMarDeRozan":"Red","EvanFournier":"Green","JJRedick":"Blue","VictorOladipo":"Magenta"}
    Mrk = {"CJMcCollum":"s","DevinBooker":"o","DonovanMitchell":"^","JimmyButler":"D","LouWilliams":"s","BradleyBeal":"o","DeMarDeRozan":"^","EvanFournier":"D","JJRedick":"s","VictorOladipo":"o"} 
    for name in playerlist:        
        plt.plot(MinutesPlayed[PlayerD[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Mrk[name], ms=7, label=name)
    plt.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))
    plt.xticks(list(range(0,7)), Month)
    plt.show()

def Pointsplot(playerlist=Players):
    Col = {"CJMcCollum":"Black","DevinBooker":"Red","DonovanMitchell":"Green","JimmyButler":"Blue","LouWilliams":"Magenta","BradleyBeal":"Black","DeMarDeRozan":"Red","EvanFournier":"Green","JJRedick":"Blue","VictorOladipo":"Magenta"}
    Mrk = {"CJMcCollum":"s","DevinBooker":"o","DonovanMitchell":"^","JimmyButler":"D","LouWilliams":"s","BradleyBeal":"o","DeMarDeRozan":"^","EvanFournier":"D","JJRedick":"s","VictorOladipo":"o"} 
    for name in playerlist:        
        plt.plot(MinutesPlayed[PlayerD[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Mrk[name], ms=7, label=name)
    plt.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))

Final Rankings - Western Conference¶

In [67]:
#Tallying up the points
McCollum_tally = sum(McCollum)
Booker_tally = sum(Booker)
Mitchell_tally = sum(Mitchell)
Butler_tally = sum(Butler)
Williams_tally = sum(Williams)

#X-Axis (Labels)
players_label = ['CJ McCollum', 'Devin Booker', 'Donovan Mitchell', 'Jimmy Butler', 'Lou Williams']
#Converting the X-Axis into an array
players_label_arr = np.array(players_label)

#Y-Axis (Values for the labels)
tally = [McCollum_tally, Booker_tally, Mitchell_tally, Butler_tally, Williams_tally]

#Plotting the Bar
plt.bar(players_label_arr, tally)

#Labelling X and Y axes
plt.xlabel('Player Names', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')
plt.ylabel('Total Points', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')

#The Title
plt.title("WC Shooting Guard - Final Rankings", fontsize=35, color="DarkBlue", fontname="Console")

#Displaying the Bar
plt.show()
